Introduction

Eunchae is a South Korean rapper under Carrie TV. She is a former member of the girl group bugAboo. In 2018, she appeared as a contestant on the survival show Produce 48 where she represented Million Market. She was eliminated in episode 8 after ranking 32nd place.
